        PRESTO on the TTC
    </h1>
    <br>
    <p id="h1line"> November 30 will be the last day the TTC will sell tickets, tokens and passes at collector booths. <br>You will still be able to use your tickets and tokens to ride the TTC after November 30.<br><br><br></p>
    
