          <h3>PRESTO</h3>
        <p id="first">PRESTO is a reloadable payment card that lets you pay your fare on the TTC, GO Transit, UP Express and 8 other transit agencies in Ontario. It’s the perfect time to get a PRESTO card to take advantage of benefits like lowest fares, balance protection, Autoload and 2-hour transfers. When you download the <a class="linked" href="/prestoAppOut">PRESTO app</a> you can load passes or money, manage up to 10 cards and check your balance.</p>
      </div>
  
