    </div> 
    <div class="col-md-5 col-md-5-set">
      <div class="para">
          <h3>Downtown Express Routes</h3>
        <p id="first">TTC customers can now use PRESTO to pay the entire fare for travel on any Downtown Express route. Just tap like you usually do and the base fare and additional Downtown Express fare will both be deducted from your PRESTO card balance.<br>
            If you’re transferring from a regular route, only the additional fare will be deducted when you tap on a Downtown Express bus. Children 12 years and under can ride Downtown Express buses for free, like they can on regular TTC routes.<br>
            If you load a TTC Monthly Pass, you can now choose to load a TTC Monthly Downtown Express Pass that allows unlimited travel on all regular TTC routes and all Downtown Express routes.<br><a class="linked" target="blank" href="http://www.ttc.ca/Fares_and_passes/Other_Passes/Downtown_Express.jsp">You can find a list of the Downtown Express routes on the TTC website.</a></p>
